optimal_awakening_growths.passive_skill_description:
ATK & DEF +200%; Ki +7 and guards all attacks for 1 turn 
from the character's entry turn; launches an additional attack 
that has a 77% chance of becoming a Super Attack; 
reduces damage received by 50%; plus an additional 
damage reduction of 10% (up to 30%) within the same turn 
with each attack received or evaded (including Super Attack); 
Ki +3 (up to +10) plus an additional ATK & DEF +30% (up to 120%) 
with each attack performed; plus an additional ATK +77% and 
performs a critical hit when activating the Active Skill or 
when Ki is 24; revives with 77% HP recovered when the character 
or an ally attacking in the same turn is KO'd (once only) 
starting from the character's next attacking turn after 
the character receives an attack 5 or more times in battle; 
plus an additional Ki +7 and ATK & DEF +77% starting from 
the turn in which the character's or an ally's Revival Skill is 
activated; guards all attacks within the next attacking turn 
after the character's Revival Skill is activated
